{"tid":2276671,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"焦點燃論 —警以「虛假陳述」拘記者 收緊查冊打壓真相？","createTime":"2020-11-08T03:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T03:25:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"344aa057024576c0f2afbb52ebf9eb9d05789bd3","tid":2276671,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"#鏗鏘集 #Appledaily #StayHome<br />\n<br />\n焦點燃論<br />\n&mdash;警以「虛假陳述」拘記者 收緊查冊打壓真相？<br />\n 蘋果日報 Apple Daily<br />\n&mdash;原刊日期：20201107<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tm1Hwwu5KOcSAVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftm1Hwwu5KOcSAVE&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft22mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=1f99c2f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tm1Hwwu5KOcSAVE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.74M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲因查冊揭發接載7.21白衣人的車主，卻因查冊被警以涉違反《道路交通條例》的「虛假陳述」被捕，保安局局長李家超聲稱出是次拘捕行動非有意針對傳媒，又指由新界北總區重案組調查蔡的案件是考慮相關警員「有經驗」處理類似案件，否認報復。<br />\n運輸署突於去年10月悄悄在查冊申請表上將目的之「其它」選項刪去，改為「其他有關交通及運輸的事宜」，到底會否任何政治目的，阻礙傳媒進行偵察報道？警方高調的拘捕行動，是否有意製造寒蟬效應？是次拘捕對傳媒有何影響？今集【焦點燃論】請來記協主席楊健興及沙田區議員黃文萱為大家剖析。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft22mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=8b5717b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft22mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=c059803c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft22mu51%2BDyw7Ma